amily. email me anyone, i feel like im going crazy here.<br /> <br />burro<br /> <br />joe im sorry this isnt important. but i still wish you were here to atleast yell at mom and dad for being such idiots that they are...</blockquote>So there you have it; just one of the many f'd up scenarios that I have lived through which is why I first made this site, which is why I'm so level-headed today. Anyway, comments are open so please give me some feedback. I need all the help I can get. Thanks.<br />
